<s> I think many types of constraints (such as resource, spatial, etc.) are very similar to world state conditions and effects and are specified in a similar way as a sentence or formula (or "pattern" as we call it) that applies at or over given time points (or temporal specifications more generally) and has given objects as elements of the formula or pattern.  </s>
